/a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of respect \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/respect\">respect</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of respite \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/respite\">respite</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of retrospect \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/retrospect\">retrospect</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of scope \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/scope\">scope</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of -scope \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/-scope\">-scope</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of scopophilia \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/scopophilia\">scopophilia</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of -scopy \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/-scopy\">-scopy</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of skeptic \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/skeptic\">skeptic</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of species \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/species\">species</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of specimen \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/specimen\">specimen</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of specious \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/specious\">specious</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of spectacle \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/spectacle\">spectacle</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of spectacular \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/spectacular\">spectacular</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of spectrum \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/spectrum\">spectrum</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of speculate \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/speculate\">speculate</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of speculation \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/speculation\">speculation</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of speculum \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/speculum\">speculum</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of spice \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/spice\">spice</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of spy \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/spy\">spy</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of suspect \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/suspect\">suspect</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of suspicion \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/suspicion\">suspicion</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of suspicious \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/suspicious\">suspicious</a>； <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of telescope \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/telescope\">telescope</a>。</p><p>它是假设的词源，其存在的证据由以下单词提供： <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">spasati</i>（梵语）“看见”； <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">spasyeiti</i>（阿维斯塔语）“窥视”； <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">skopein</i>（希腊语）“看，观察”， <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">skeptesthai</i> “看”， <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">skopos</i> “观察者，监视者”； <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">specere</i>（拉丁语）“看”； <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">spehhon</i>（古高地德语）“窥视”， <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">spähen</i>（德语）“窥视”。</p>"
